Restore a Previous Version of a Recipe

Test new ideas on recipes in CRM Analytics. If you break a recipe, you can revert to a previous version.

To view a recipe's version history, click the Version History button. 
To view a previous version, click the date of the version.
To make sure you don't lose changes to a version, save the changes before switching to another version.
Data Prep can store up to 20 versions for each recipeâ€”10 with descriptions and 10 without.
The latest versions are always kept.
title: Reverting to Previous Versions of Recipes in CRM Analytics
